Check_Divisible
Check if a Number is Even and Divisible by 5
Sample Input
20
Sample Output
Even and Divisible by 5


#include<stdio.h>
int main(){
    int a;
    scanf("%d", &a);

    (a%5 == 0) ? printf("Even and Divisible by 5") : printf("Not both Even and Divisible by 5");
}



